Start
/ Test: verify fails when Created is older than timeout setting
- archive identity 'testSigner', force, on error ignore
- create identity testSigner
- set %data% = { "payload": "old" }
- sign %data%
- set signing timeout to 50
- wait for 60 ms
- verify %data% with contracts ['C0'], on error call HandleTimedOut
- assert %timedOut% is true, "signature older than timeout should fail"

HandleTimedOut
- set %timedOut% = true
